Rstudio

Integrated Development Editor

Layout, 4 panels

Features

  • Package management
  • Console to run R, with syntax highligther
  • Editor to work with scripts / markdown
  • autocompletion using TAB
  • Cheatsheets
  • Keyboard shortcuts
